      <p>Your safety matters to us. Please read the following information before using 3DWhiteningStrips teeth whitening strips.</p>

      <h2>Intended Use</h2>
      <p>Our whitening strips are designed for cosmetic teeth whitening in adults. They use an enamel-safe, low-sensitivity formula.</p>

      <h2>How to Use Safely</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Apply one strip to your upper teeth and one to your lower teeth.</li>
        <li>Leave on for 30 minutes, once daily, for up to 7 days.</li>
        <li>Do not swallow the gel. Avoid eating or drinking while wearing the strips.</li>
        <li>Rinse your mouth after removing the strips.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Warnings &amp; Precautions</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Keep out of reach of children. Not intended for children under 12.</li>
        <li>If you are pregnant, nursing, or have dental concerns (gum disease, braces, crowns), consult your dentist before use.</li>
        <li>Discontinue use if you experience irritation, discomfort, or unusual sensitivity, and consult a dental professional.</li>
        <li>Do not use on damaged or decayed teeth.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Storage</h2>
      <p>Store in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight. Do not use after the expiry date printed on the packaging.</p>

